comments: Clarke (MEM) slightly extends his hands into Okoro (CLE) during the pick and the contact is marginal.
Okoro (CLE) makes contact with the ball during Anderson's (MEM) driving shot attempt.
Drummond (CLE) makes contact to Valanciunas' (MEM) arm that affects his shot attempt.
Okoro (CLE) briefly rests his forearm on Jones' (MEM) front as he loses control of the ball during his dribble. The contact is marginal.
Following the turnover, Jones (MEM) reaches in and makes contact to Osman's (CLE) arm that affects his SQBR in transition.
During the pick, Drummond (CLE) turns and slightly extends his arm into Anderson's (MEM) arm as he begins to move towards the rim. The contact is marginal.
Jones (MEM) makes contact with the ball and deflects the pass intended for Drummond (CLE).
The ball is thrown off of Anderson's (MEM) foot and he does not intentionally kick it.
Brooks (MEM) briefly engages in marginal contact with Dotson (CLE) after he makes contact with the loose ball.

Replay review of the shooting foul called on Okoro (CLE) pursuant to a coach?s challenge was deemed successful.  Jones (MEM) creates the marginal contact by extending his arm towards Okoro, who makes no illegal contact on the play.
Valanciunas (MEM) establishes himself in a legal position in Osman's (CLE) path and he absorbs the oncoming contact during the off ball screen.
Osman (CLE) avoids making contact to Bane's (MEM) arm during his jump shot attempt.
Anderson (MEM) commits a take foul on Dotson (CLE).
